LACHAISE was rated on the inside, saved ground through the far turn, was asked at the quarter-pole, chased under a drive into the final furlong and weakened. FREEDOM TRAIL raced in the three path on the first turn, stalked the pace on the outside, issued a challenge in the two to three path on the far turn, lost touch with the winner under a drive in upper stretch, dropped back into the final furlong and also weakened. CONGRUENT checked while tossing his head rankly off heels nearing the first turn, tossed his head again while three then four wide going around that bend, threw his head yet again while dragging his way forward leaving the backstretch, was rated on the outside, went three to four wide while roused on the far turn, spun five wide into the stretch and lacked the needed kick. BELOUNI (FR) was taken under a tight hold early, tugged eagerly on the bit while two then three wide on the first turn, remained under stout restraint onto the backstretch then settled more kindly at the rear, went three wide for most of the far turn then shifted five wide, came six wide into the stretch and lacked the needed response.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: BELMONT PARK RACE 10 1 1/16M Turf CR: 74. Maiden Claiming Purse 45000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD FOALED IN NEW YORK STATE AND APPROVED BY THE NEW YORK STATE-BRED REGISTRY. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 125 lbs. Claiming Price $40,000 (1.5% Aftercare Assessment Due At Time Of Claim Otherwise Claim Will Be V oid). (If the Stewards consider it inadvisable to run this race on the turf course, this race will be run at One Mile and One Sixteenth on the Main Track.) (Rail at 27 feet).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: THETHRILLOFVICTORY broke out at the start bumping SEA CRUISE, chased just off the inside from near the rear of the field early on, advanced into the far turn and came under coaxing at the three-eighths, spun three wide into upper stretch, rallied to take command a furlong out, then drew clear through to the finish kept to task. JUST FOR LUCK three wide in pursuit, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled out five wide into upper stretch, proved no match for the top one while offering up a mild kick to secure the place honors. ATLANTA'S ACUNA forwardly placed from the start, got eased off when pulling on the bit into the backstretch to settle three then two wide in closest aim of the leader, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled three to four wide into upper stretch and took over the front straightened away, dug in and was collared a furlong out, kept on to preserve the show honors by a nostril on the wire. BAD LARRY three to four wide in pursuit from just off the pace, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled five wide into upper stretch, offered up a bid a furlong out, kept on to just miss for the show honors. BARRY THE BUILDER just off the inside tracking from just off the pace, tucked inside through the far turn and came under coaxing at the three-eighths, spun just off the inside into upper stretch and weakened in the late stages. FLUORESCENT BAY chased three wide down the backstretch and then four to five wide through the far turn coaxed along from three furlongs out, went seven to eight wide into upper stretch and improved position to the finish. HARI chased just off the inside until tucked inside into the far turn, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled four wide into upper stretch, offered up a bid a furlong out then flattened out through to the end. WAR PRINCE four then three wide in pursuit, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled four to five wide into upper stretch and weakened. SILENT RUNNING chased three to four wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, angled six wide into upper stretch, weakened. SOMAMA BEACH pulled early on against the restraint of the rider taking command and forcing ATLANTA'S ACUNA to ease off into the backstretch, settled to cut the pace from the two path through swift splits, tucked inside into the far turn and came under coaxing near the five-sixteenths, came under challenge and took the inside route into upper stretch, yielded the front straightened away and tired. HOLDING AU PAIR sluggish early on, grew detached at the tail of the field and gave chase along the inside, continued into upper stretch along the inside and was lightly ridden along and tapped a few times while making no impact. SEA CRUISE got bumped at the start by THETHRILLOFVICTORY, chased four to five wide under coaxing from the three-eighths, retreated and went four wide into upper stretch having gave way, then got eased home to the finish.
